Double words are a list which have the same first letter on each word The left column are the
order in which I collected them starting from when I was in hospital at the start of 2003 to the
almost present day 2006 This is a hard to find subject on the web I found one other small site
under initially related maybe its some kind of taboo subject

Double Word Double Words Bi-Word Word Pair Same first Letter Dual Words Ohter type of word usage in double words said offen is double word used in machine langauge lot 'C' Programers still use the Lingo An Because of That Makes very Hard searching on Web For anything Simular to This Site I wrote a program to collect them automatic from clipboard txt's but felt could be wrote better still not got back into it Like less holdups on big txt an a more continuous theme which is posiable..

All if you like other ways play words like many people come this site do Try This
